    <lb n="1"/>αυτη. καὶ γὰρ ἀπὸ τῆς ἐκείνου οἰκίας ἐξεληλύθει πεφαρμακεῦσθαι 

    <lb n="2"/>λέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γω</supplied>ν καὶ ἀπ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὸ</supplied> μὲν τῆς Ἑρμιόνης οἰκίας ἐξιὼν οὔτ᾽ ἔφη 

    <lb n="3"/>πρός τινα αἰσθέσθαι οὐδενὸς οὐδ᾽ ὅλως ὑπόνοιαν οὐδεμίαν ἔσχεν, 

    <lb n="4"/>ἀπὸ δὲ τῆς ἑαυτοῦ τε καὶ τοῦ κληρονομεῖν μέλλοντος υἱοῦ 

    <lb n="5"/>προῆλθε πεφαρμακεῦσθαι λέγων. εἶχεν μὲν οὖν αἰτίας τοῦ καὶ 

    <lb n="6"/>αὐτὸς <subst><add place="inline">ἑ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αυ</supplied>τῷ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">α<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αυ</supplied>τω</del></subst> <choice><corr>προσενεγκεῖν</corr><sic>προσενενκειν</sic></choice> φάρμακον ἃς καὶ ἄλλοι πολλοὶ τὸν 

    <lb n="7"/>θάνατον τοῦ ζῆν <choice><corr>προκρίναντες</corr><sic>προκρειναντες</sic></choice>, καὶ γὰρ ὑπὸ δανειστῶν ὤλλυ-

    <lb n="8"/>το καὶ ἠπόρει. εἰ δ᾽ ἄρα τις καὶ ἐπεβούλευσεν αὐτῷ ὁ υἱὸς ἐπιτηδει-

    <lb n="9"/>ό<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τα</unclear>τος. διὰ τί <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear>᾽ <choice><corr>ἐπήνεγκεν</corr><sic>επηνενκεν</sic></choice> τὸ ἔνκλημα ταύτῃ δῆλον. δύναται 

    <lb n="10"/>μὲν γὰρ καὶ ἄ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λλ</unclear>α τινὰ <choice><corr>λελυπῆσθαι</corr><sic>λελοιπησθαι</sic></choice> παρὰ τὸν τῆς προνοίας χρόνον, 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>διαδείκνυσι</corr><sic>διαδικνυσι</sic></choice> <add place="supralinear">δὲ</add> τὸ πρᾶγμα ὅτι καὶ ἐζηλοτύπει αὐτὴν μὴ ἐπισταμένην 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ ἄνδρα μὲν αὐτῆς ἑαυτὸν ἐκάλει, οὐκ ἀξιούμενος δὲ ταύτης 

    <lb n="13"/>τῆς προσηγορίας ὑπ᾽ αὐτῆς καὶ <subst><add place="inline">ἐρωτικ<add place="supralinear">ῶ</add>ς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ερωτικος</del></subst> ἤλγει καὶ ἐπιζῆν ἑαυτῷ 

    <lb n="14"/>ταύτην οὐκ ἤθελεν <g type="slanting-stroke"/> <g type="slanting-stroke"/>. ἐὰν λέγωσιν δοῦλον Σμάραγδον ἀνεύρετον 

    <lb n="15"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γε</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γ</supplied>ονέ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>αι αὐτὸν αἰτίαν ἔχοντα τοῦ τὴν πίστιν κεκλοφέναι <g type="slanting-stroke"/> <g type="slanting-stroke"/>, 

    <lb n="16"/>φη<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὶν</unclear> δ᾽ οὖν καὶ πίστιν γεγονέναι ἵνα κλεπῇ, οὐ δύναται γὰρ κεκλέ-

    <lb n="17"/>φθαι τὸ μηδ᾽ ἀρχὴν γενόμενον μὴ δυνατὸν δ᾽ εἶναι μηδὲ 

    <lb n="18"/>πίστιν γεγρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ά</supplied>φθαι. οὔτε γὰρ ἡ <choice><corr>ἀγοράσ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ασ</supplied>α</corr><sic>αγορασα</sic></choice> γράμματα ᾔδει οὔτε ἡ νῦν 

    <lb n="19"/>ἐνκαλουμένη Ἑρμιόνη, οὔτε ξένος οὐδεὶς ἄλλης καταγραφείσης 

    <lb n="20"/>πίστ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ν π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ᾽ ἑ</supplied>αυτοῦ δίδωσι. ὥστε καὶ παρὰ τίνος ἂν εἴποι τὴν πίστιν 

    <lb n="21"/>ἐσχηκέναι; παρὰ παντὸς γὰρ ἄκυρος ἦν. εἰ δὲ ἀπέδρα δοῦλος 


    <lb n="22"/>οὐδὲν δύναται τοῦτο κατὰ δεσπότου. ἔτι μέντοι <subst><add place="inline">περὶ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ερι</del></subst> τοῦ 

    <lb n="23"/>μηδὲ πίστιν εἶναι καὶ ἡ νομὴ συνβάλλεται. τῶν γὰρ ἐν πίστει 

    <lb n="24"/>καταγραφ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">έ</unclear>ντων τὸ ὄνομα μ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ό</supplied>νον εἰς τοὺς χρηματισμοὺς 

    <lb n="25"/>παρε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θ</supplied>έ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ντ</unclear>ων, <choice><corr>οὔπω</corr><sic>ουκετι</sic></choice> δ᾽ ἀντιποιουμένων ὧν κατεγράφησαν 

    <lb n="26"/>ἡ μὲν <choice><corr>ἀγοράσ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ασ</supplied>α</corr><sic>αγορασα</sic></choice> φανε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρά</unclear> ἐσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τι</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> καὶ ἀντιπεποιημένη καὶ ἀφ᾽ οὗπερ 

    <lb n="27"/>ἠγόρα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied>ε <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κ</supplied>αρπουμένη, ὁ δ᾽ ἀφ᾽ οὗπερ πέπρακε οὐκέτι ἀλλὰ καὶ 

    <lb n="28"/>τῶν τῆς μητρὸς τὴν <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">οἰ</supplied>κονομίαν ὡς προνοητὴς ποιούμενος 

    <lb n="29"/>τούτ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οι</unclear>[ς <app type="editorial"><lem>δ᾽ οὐκ</lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δὲ</supplied></rdg></app>] ἐνχ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ει</supplied>ρῶν <g type="slanting-stroke"/> <g type="slanting-stroke"/>. ἐὰν κοινόν ὁμολόγημα λέγωσι γεγο-

    <lb n="30"/>νέναι τῆς θυγατρὸς πρὸς τὴν Ἑρμιόνην ἑκατὸν πεντήκοντα <num value="150"/> 

    <lb n="31"/>κεραμίω<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> καὶ ἀπὸ τούτων ὧν ἠγόρασεν κτημάτων φαμε`ν 

    <lb n="32"/>τοῦτο <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">πᾶ</supplied>ν μηδὲν εἶναι πρὸς τὸν κατήγορον. οὐ γὰρ <subst><add place="inline">εἴ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/></del></subst> τι ἔπραξε 

    <lb n="33"/>θυγάτηρ πρὸς τὴν μητέρα τοῦτο αὐτοῖς εἰς συκοφαντίαν εὕρημα, 

    <lb n="34"/>ὅμως δὲ οὔτε τῶν αὐτῶν χρόνων οὐδὲ τοῦτο ἀλλὰ μετ᾽ ἐνι-

    <lb n="35"/>αυτὸ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> <choice><corr>ἐγγὺς</corr><sic>ενγυς</sic></choice> δὴ οὔτε ἑκ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ατὸ</supplied>ν πεντήκοντα <num value="150"/> κεραμίων χορηγία 

    <lb n="36"/>πρὸς πίστ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ν τεσσάρων <num value="4"/> ταλάντων οὐδὲν ἐστι, ταῦτα γὰρ μόνο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> 

    <lb n="37"/>ἑνὸς <num value="1"/> ἐστιν τόκος. ἀλλὰ μ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὴν</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>υ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τω</unclear>ν πίστεως περὶ τούτων 

    <lb n="38"/>οὔσης παρὰ τῷ δοκοῦντι πεπρακέναι ἑτέρῳ ἂν ἑαυτὴ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> γράμ-

    <lb n="39"/>ματι ἡ θ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υγ</supplied>άτηρ <choice><corr>κατηγγύα</corr><sic>κατηνγυα</sic></choice> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τῷ</unclear> δημοσίῳ μελλήσουσα ἀφαιρε-

    <lb n="40"/>θήσε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σθαι ὁ</supplied>πότε ἐκείνῳ ἐδόκει; ἀλλὰ καὶ τὸ τῆς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χορ</supplied>ηγίας τοιοῦτον 

    <lb n="41"/>ἦν· <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῇ γὰρ Ἑρμι</supplied>όνῃ τρεῖς <num value="3"/> παῖδες ἦσαν, Ἀ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φ</unclear>ρο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="7" unit="character"/>ν, Διονυσία, 

    <lb n="42"/>τ<gap reason="lost" extent="11" unit="character"/>ν τῆς Διονυσίας τὸ πρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="10" unit="character"/> Ἑρμιόνη 

    <lb n="43"/><gap reason="lost" extent="14" unit="character"/> ἔκστασιν τοῦ μη<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="12" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear>ν 

    <lb n="44"/><gap reason="lost" extent="16" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ης</unclear><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="17" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τερ</unclear>ου 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="3" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="45"/>τῶν παίδων τοῦ πρεσβυτέρου, 

    <lb n="46"/>ἐδεήθη ἡ Διονυσία τῆς μητρὸς 

    <lb n="47"/>μὴ ἐπὶ μόνοις αὐτὴν ἀπολιπεῖν 

    <lb n="48"/>τοῖς <choice><corr cert="low">διαταγῆναι</corr><sic>δια<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ηγηναι</sic></choice> <subst><add place="inline">φθάσασ<add place="supralinear">ιν</add></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">φθασασιν</del></subst> 

    <lb n="49"/>ἀλλά τι καὶ παρασχεῖν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὡ</unclear>ς ἐπὶ 

    <lb n="50"/>ἑνὶ <num value="1"/> μόνῳ σαλεύουσαν, καὶ ἡ μὲν 

    <lb n="51"/>Ἑρμιόνη δίδωσιν αὐτῇ ἓ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> ἥμισυ <num value="1  1/2 "/> 

    <lb n="52"/>τάλαντον. ἡ δ᾽ ἵνα μὴ καὶ ζῶσα 

    <lb n="53"/>ἡ μήτηρ τούτων στερῆται δίδωσι 

    <lb n="54"/>ἀντὶ τόκου κατ᾽ ἐνιαυτὸν τὴν 

    <lb n="55"/>χορηγίαν ταύτην καὶ τοῦτο αὐτὸ 

    <lb n="56"/>γέγραπται κατὰ τὸ <subst><add place="inline">κοινὸν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>κινον</del></subst> ὁμολό-

    <lb n="57"/>γημα. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.20607" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20607" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notAfter="0131-10-10">vor 10. Okt. 131</date></p></div><div n="meta.20607" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. Thomas, Roman Epistrategos, S. 187.</p></div><div n="meta.20607" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">472</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">20607</biblScope><xref type="LDAB" href="20607" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in LDAB</xref></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">472</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;3;472" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20607" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.20607" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Kol. II 22-29: M.Chr. 235</bibl></div><div n="meta.20607" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>